agentData.mission: Create a single canonical entrypoint command (or confirm and wire up the existing one from agent outputs) that runs: preflight -> artifact gate -> taxonomy validator -> toy meta-analysis -> manifest writer. It must write runtime/_build/manifest.json and runtime/_build/logs/run.log and exit non-zero on failure. This is needed because many overlapping runner/gate scripts exist across agent directories but no standardized one-command execution exists in practice.
